{
  "_tutorial_zh": [
    "=== 武器注册配置 ===",
    "此文件定义新武器的基础属性",
    "武器在游戏启动时自动注册，tooltips和lang自动生成",
    "",
    "字段说明：",
    "  id: 武器ID，注册为 bstweaker_<id>，同时作为默认显示名称",
    "  type: 武器类型 (dagger/hammer/spear/battleaxe/nunchaku)",
    "  texture: 纹理ID，对应 cfg/textures/item<texture>.png",
    "  material: 材质属性",
    "    harvestLevel: 挖掘等级 (0=木,1=石,2=铁,3=钻石)",
    "    durability: 耐久度",
    "    damage: 基础伤害",
    "    enchantability: 附魔能力",
    "  damageModifier: 额外伤害 (可选)",
    "  speedModifier: 攻速修正 (可选)",
    "",
    "自动生成 (可在mod配置中关闭)：",
    "  - tooltips.json 条目",
    "  - lang 翻译 (追加模式)",
    "  - 模型 (关闭后可使用自定义模型)"
  ],
  "_tutorial_en": [
    "=== Weapon Registration Config ===",
    "This file defines new weapon properties",
    "Weapons auto-register on startup, tooltips and lang auto-generated",
    "",
    "Fields:",
    "  id: Weapon ID, registers as bstweaker_<id>, used as default name",
    "  type: Weapon type (dagger/hammer/spear/battleaxe/nunchaku)",
    "  texture: Texture ID, maps to cfg/textures/item<texture>.png",
    "  material: Material properties",
    "    harvestLevel: Mining level (0=wood,1=stone,2=iron,3=diamond)",
    "    durability: Durability",
    "    damage: Base damage",
    "    enchantability: Enchantability",
    "  damageModifier: Extra damage (optional)",
    "  speedModifier: Speed modifier (optional)",
    "",
    "Auto-generated (toggle in mod config):",
    "  - tooltips.json entries",
    "  - lang translations (append mode)",
    "  - models (disable to use custom models)"
  ],
